<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٤٤٧٨ - <span class="c2">«كسر عظم الميت٤ ككسره حيا»</span> .<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
